            'en' => '<p><strong>Mandatory conditions when concluding a service contract:</strong><br>- Prepayment in the amount of 30% of the cost under the contract is made within 10 banking days from the date of signing the contract. Final payment in the amount of 70% of the cost of services under the order within 10 banking days from the date of delivery of goods, acceptance of e-invoice</p><p>- proposed prices in the bid shall be valid until December 31, 2024</p><p>- currency of the tender – US dollars. In the case of winning by the local company, its bid will be transformed into national currency at the rate of the Central Bank of Uzbekistan on the date of acceptance and inscribed into the contract.</p><p><strong>In order to register a bid for participation it is necessary to send to the e-mail specified below:</strong><br>1. A scan of a free-form letter on the letterhead of the participating company with a contact person (please specify in your application which lot you will participate in);<br>2. A scan of the signed NDA (download link below);<br>3. Scan of the certificate of state registration of Company.</p><p><strong>Responsible manager:</strong><br>Shukhrat Rizakulov<br>Procurement Manager of RWC LLC</p><p><strong>Contacts:</strong><br>Tel.: +998 90 357-77-80 (WhatsApp, Telegram)<br>E-mail: rshukhrat@perfectum.uz</p><p>Deadline of the application submission: Applications will be accepted until 15:00 (Tashkent time) 10.06.2024.</p>',
